<br>
Sometime, take a few minutes and look at the class boards of the other classes.  I think you'll probably be shocked at what you see....<br>
<br>
For all of its flaws from time to time, IMHO, these boards are among the best organized and most productive (if the most angry, from time to time.  =P) of the class boards, certainly the best of the &quot;Offensive Class&quot; boards.  I came here looking for about a half dozen pieces of information for some research I'm doing elsewhere... and unlike Graffes, the Ranger Glade, The Steel Warriors, Monkly Business and even The Safehouse (to name a few), I was able to find what I was looking for in all of 90 seconds.<br>
<br>
That's really tremendous.<br>
<br>
You want AA discussions?  These boards have them.  DPS parses, outlines, theorizing?  Got those, too.  Analysis of balance complaints, both by and about other classes?  Easy.  Parchment drops, spell lists... it goes on and on.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I just thought you all deserved some credit for that (and the mods especially).<br>
<br>
Back to that work thing.  And I'm glad to see that the class is still here.  Back in March, a few of you had me wondering... =P  <br>
<br>
Just kidding.  Take care, and keep up the good work.<br>
